{
  "page": "Clayton Suggs",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the suitor of Rohanne Webber, see <a href=\"/index.php/Cleyton_Caswell\" title=\"Cleyton Caswell\">Cleyton Caswell</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Suggs\" title=\"House Suggs\"><img alt=\"House Suggs.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/8a/House_Suggs.svg/50px-House_Suggs.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8a/House_Suggs.svg/75px-House_Suggs.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8a/House_Suggs.svg/100px-House_Suggs.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Clayton Suggs</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Suggs\" title=\"House Suggs\"><img alt=\"House Suggs.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/8a/House_Suggs.svg/50px-House_Suggs.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8a/House_Suggs.svg/75px-House_Suggs.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8a/House_Suggs.svg/100px-House_Suggs.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:SerClaytonSuggs_by_KevinMcCoy.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SerClaytonSuggs by KevinMcCoy.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/SerClaytonSuggs_by_KevinMcCoy.jpg/350px-SerClaytonSuggs_by_KevinMcCoy.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"453\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/SerClaytonSuggs_by_KevinMcCoy.jpg/525px-SerClaytonSuggs_by_KevinMcCoy.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ad/SerClaytonSuggs_by_KevinMcCoy.jpg/700px-SerClaytonSuggs_by_KevinMcCoy.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Ser Clayton Suggs - by Kevin McCoy ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Suggs\" title=\"House Suggs\">House Suggs</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_Dragonstone\" title=\"House Baratheon of Dragonstone\">House Baratheon of Dragonstone</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Queen%27s_men\" title=\"Queen&#39;s men\">Queen's men</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Flea_Bottom\" title=\"Flea Bottom\">Flea Bottom</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> (appears)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Clayton Suggs</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Suggs\" title=\"House Suggs\">House Suggs</a>, and a supporter of <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> His coat of arms is a winged pig.<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Clayton\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Clayton</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Clayton\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Clayton</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Behind_the_Scenes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Behind the Scenes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clayton_Suggs&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Clayton is a short, burly man, with a balding head<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and a mouthful of broken brown teeth.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> He has pig eyes, and blackheads on his nose.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> Clayton has a deep voice.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> He is older than Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Harwood_Fell\" title=\"Harwood Fell\">Harwood Fell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Clayton is considered a crony<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> and the strong right hand of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Godry_Farring\" title=\"Godry Farring\">Godry Farring</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> He is strong and courageous, but also crude and brutish.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>  Clayton is cruel and enjoys <a href=\"/index.php/Torture\" title=\"Torture\">torturing</a>, and his love for the <a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">Lord of Light</a> may only be love of human sacrifice.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clayton_Suggs&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Clayton was a <a href=\"/index.php/Hedge_knight\" title=\"Hedge knight\">hedge knight</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> of <a href=\"/index.php/Lowborn\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lowborn\">lowborn</a> origin,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_clayton_suggs.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_clayton_suggs.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> hailing from <a href=\"/index.php/Flea_Bottom\" title=\"Flea Bottom\">Flea Bottom</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>. According to Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Justin_Massey\" title=\"Justin Massey\">Justin Massey</a>, Clayton gambled with <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Torture\" title=\"Torture\">torturers</a>, and aided them in the questioning of prisoners, especially young women.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clayton_Suggs&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clayton_Suggs&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ser Clayton is sworn to King <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>. He is among the <a href=\"/index.php/Queen%27s_men\" title=\"Queen&#39;s men\">queen's men</a> who goes north to the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a> with Stannis.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clayton_Suggs&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Marc_Fishman_Riders.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a7/Marc_Fishman_Riders.jpg/350px-Marc_Fishman_Riders.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"240\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a7/Marc_Fishman_Riders.jpg/525px-Marc_Fishman_Riders.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a7/Marc_Fishman_Riders.jpg/700px-Marc_Fishman_Riders.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Marc_Fishman_Riders.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Suggs rips his longsword from its scabbard - by Marc Fishman ©</div></div></div>\n<p>Clayton is part of Stannis's honor guard when <a href=\"/index.php/Free_folk\" title=\"Free folk\">free folk</a> pass through the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a> after the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_beneath_the_Wall\" title=\"Battle beneath the Wall\">battle beneath the Wall</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> During Stannis's war council, Clayton states that Houses <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hornwood\" title=\"House Hornwood\">Hornwood</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Cerwyn\" title=\"House Cerwyn\">Cerwyn</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tallhart\" title=\"House Tallhart\">Tallhart</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Ryswell\" title=\"House Ryswell\">Ryswell</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dustin\" title=\"House Dustin\">Dustin</a> are all <a href=\"/index.php/Traitor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Traitor\">traitors</a> and lapdogs of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannisters</a>. When Stannis dismisses his men during a meeting with <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Night&#39;s Watch\">Lord Commander of the Night's Watch</a>, Clayton mutters something to <a href=\"/index.php/Harwood_Fell\" title=\"Harwood Fell\">Harwood Fell</a> that makes him laugh.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When Stannis's army is slowed during the <a href=\"/index.php/March_on_Winterfell\" title=\"March on Winterfell\">march on Winterfell</a>, Clayton agrees with Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Godry_Farring\" title=\"Godry Farring\">Godry Farring</a> they should burn someone to appease <a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">R'hllor</a> and end the blizzard, but the king refuses.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Asha Greyjoy</a> fears Clayton will burn her because of her king's blood, as her father <a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Balon Greyjoy\">Balon</a> was <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Isles_and_the_North\" title=\"King of the Isles and the North\">King of the Isles and the North</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When four <a href=\"/index.php/House_Peasebury\" title=\"House Peasebury\">Peasebury</a> men are caught committing <a href=\"/index.php/Cannibalism\" title=\"Cannibalism\">cannibalism</a> at a <a href=\"/index.php/Crofters%27_village\" title=\"Crofters&#39; village\">crofters' village</a>, they are to be burned alive as a sacrifice to R'hllor. Desiring a quick death, their serjeant insults the queen's men. The serjeant calls Clayton a \"bleeding <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a>\", goading him into quickly killing the condemned man with a knife.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> Clayton insults Asha after the sacrifices are burned, but he is interrupted by <a href=\"/index.php/Alysane_Mormont\" title=\"Alysane Mormont\">Alysane Mormont</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Justin_Massey\" title=\"Justin Massey\">Justin Massey</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When Asha later reminds Clayton that Stannis <a href=\"/index.php/Eunuch\" title=\"Eunuch\">gelds</a> men for rape, he laughs and says he would sooner see her burn.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> When they hear riders approaching the village, Clayton tells Asha to run and warn the king, as he assumes it is Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a>'s host upon them. However, the riders turn out to be <a href=\"/index.php/Tycho_Nestoris\" title=\"Tycho Nestoris\">Tycho Nestoris</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Bank_of_Braavos\" title=\"Iron Bank of Braavos\">Iron Bank of Braavos</a>, and his escort, some of whom are Asha's <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> men from <a href=\"/index.php/Deepwood_Motte\" title=\"Deepwood Motte\">Deepwood Motte</a>.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clayton_Suggs&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Clayton is present along with Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Godry_Farring\" title=\"Godry Farring\">Godry Farring</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Richard_Horpe\" title=\"Richard Horpe\">Richard Horpe</a> when Stannis interrogates Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Tybald\" title=\"Tybald\">Tybald</a> about his loyalties. Stannis has Clayton threaten violence on the <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">maester</a> to make Tybald tell him everything. Clayton wants Stannis to burn <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Clayton\">Quotes by Clayton</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clayton_Suggs&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Clayton\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Godry</b>: I had forgotten that you <a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">northmen</a> worship <a href=\"/index.php/Heart_tree\" title=\"Heart tree\">trees</a>.<br />\n<b>Clayton</b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Old_gods\" title=\"Old gods\">What sort of god</a> lets himself be pissed upon by dogs?<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Godry_Farring\" title=\"Godry Farring\">Godry Farring</a> and Clayton to <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>A sacrifice will prove <a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">our faith</a> still burns true, Sire.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Clayton to <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Clayton\">Quotes about Clayton</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clayton_Suggs&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Clayton\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Suggs was an upjumped <a href=\"/index.php/Hedge_knight\" title=\"Hedge knight\">hedge knight</a>, as crude as he was strong.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>She had seen him at the nightfires, watching, his lips parted and his eyes avid. It is not <a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">the god</a> he loves, it is the flames, she concluded.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Asha Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Some men had faces that cried out for a beard. Ser Clayton's face cried out for an axe between the eyes.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Asha Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>He learned all he knows in the wynds of <a href=\"/index.php/Flea_Bottom\" title=\"Flea Bottom\">Flea Bottom</a>. Were I to put you in his charge, he might strangle you with your own chain or scoop your eye out with a spoon.<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Tybald\" title=\"Tybald\">Tybald</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clayton_Suggs&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Clayton Suggs may be a reference to American football players <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Terrell_Suggs\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Terrell Suggs\">Terrell Suggs</a> and <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mark_Clayton_(American_Football,_born_1961)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Mark Clayton (American Football, born 1961)\">Mark Clayton</a> of the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Baltimore_Ravens\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Baltimore Ravens\">Baltimore Ravens</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clayton_Suggs&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The Citadel. Heraldry: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/Heraldry/Houses/10/\">Houses from an unknown region</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-TWOW-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-TWOW_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-TWOW_3-1\">3.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-TWOW_3-2\">3.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-TWOW_3-3\">3.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_I_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Theon I (The Winds of Winter)\">Theon I</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">4.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\">4.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.